<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>K3RN.LABS — Maquette B : Galerie Immersive</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #000000;
            --bg-secondary: #0F0F0F;
            --bg-card: #1A1A1A;
            --bg-card-hover: #22242B;
            --surface-1: #2F323A;
            --surface-2: #5D5C5B;
            --border-subtle: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            --border-default: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            --border-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            --text-primary: #FAFAFA;
            --text-secondary: #A1A1AA;
            --text-muted: #71717A;
            --brand-primary: #F75105;
            --brand-secondary: #F78E21;
            --shadow-glow: 0 0 30px rgba(247,81,5,0.3);
            --radius-md: 8px;
            --radius-lg: 12px;
            --radius-xl: 16px;
            --radius-2xl: 24px;
            --radius-full: 9999px;
            --space-1: 4px; --space-2: 8px; --space-3: 12px; --space-4: 16px;
            --space-6: 24px; --space-8: 32px; --space-12: 48px; --space-16: 64px;
            --color-go: #22C55E; --color-explore: #F59E0B; --color-park: #6B7280; --color-kill: #EF4444;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        ::selection { background: rgba(247,81,5,0.3); color: white; }

        /* ═══════ HEADER ═══════ */
        .header {
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }
        .header-inner {
            max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            height: 64px; padding: 0 var(--space-8);
        }
        .header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-6); }
        .logo {
            width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--brand-primary);
            border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; color: white;
            transition: transform 0.5s;
        }
        .logo:hover { transform: rotate(180deg); }
        .nav-divider { width: 1px; height: 20px; background: var(--border-default); }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-6); }
        .nav-link {
            font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none;
            padding: 20px 0; position: relative; transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-link:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
        .nav-link.active { color: var(--brand-primary); }
        .nav-link.active::after {
            content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 2px; background: var(--brand-primary);
        }
        .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-3); }
        .header-btn {
            padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);
            background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .header-btn:hover { color: var(--text-primary); border-color: var(--border-strong); background: var(--bg-card); }
        .avatar {
            width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--surface-1); border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .main { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8) var(--space-16); }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl); padding: var(--space-8);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--brand-primary);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        }

        /* ═══════ FEATURED PROJECT ═══════ */
        .featured {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-8);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
            min-height: 520px;
        }

        /* Radar Container */
        .radar-container {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            padding: var(--space-8);
        }
        .radar-svg {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 360px;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
        }
        .radar-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: var(--space-6);
            left: var(--space-6);
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
            padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid;
        }
        .badge-go { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #4ade80; border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
        .badge-explore { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: #fbbf24; border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.2); }
        .badge-park { background: rgba(107,114,128,0.1); color: #9ca3af; border-color: rgba(107,114,128,0.2); }
        .badge-kill { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #f87171; border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.2); }

        /* Details Side */
        .featured-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .featured-details h2 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
        }
        .featured-details .description {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        }
        .separator {
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border-subtle);
            margin: var(--space-6) 0;
        }

        /* Axis Bars */
        .axis-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-3);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
        }
        .axis-label {
            width: 120px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .axis-track {
            flex: 1;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--surface-1);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .axis-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            transition: width 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        .axis-score {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
            min-width: 36px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .btn-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-3);
            margin-top: var(--space-8);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);
            padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
            background: var(--brand-primary); color: white; border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600;
            font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--brand-secondary); box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);
            padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
            background: transparent; color: var(--text-primary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
            font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--bg-card); border-color: var(--border-strong); }

        /* ═══════ CAROUSEL ═══════ */
        .carousel-section {
            margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
        }
        .carousel-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        }
        .carousel-header h3 {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        .carousel-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-2);
        }
        .carousel-nav button {
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md); color: var(--text-muted);
            cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .carousel-nav button:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary); border-color: var(--border-strong); background: var(--bg-card);
        }
        .carousel-track {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-6);
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 85%, transparent 100%);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 85%, transparent 100%);
        }
        .carousel-track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

        .mini-card {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 220px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            padding: var(--space-6);
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mini-card:hover {
            background: var(--bg-card-hover);
            border-color: var(--border-strong);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        .mini-card .accent-band {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 3px;
        }
        .mini-card .mini-title {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
            margin-top: var(--space-2);
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mini-card .mini-desc {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mini-card .mini-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .mini-card .mini-score {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        }
        .mini-card .mini-score .unit {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ═══════ INSIGHTS ═══════ */
        .insights-list {
            list-style: none;
        }
        .insight-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: var(--space-3);
            padding: var(--space-3) 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }
        .insight-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .insight-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 20px; height: 20px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .insight-text {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .insight-text strong {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .maquette-label {
            position: fixed; top: var(--space-6); right: var(--space-6); z-index: 100;
            background: var(--brand-primary); color: white;
            padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em; box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .animate-in { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards; opacity: 0; }
        .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.45s; }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .featured { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .main { padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-4); }
            .card { padding: var(--space-6); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="maquette-label">Maquette B / Galerie Immersive</div>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-inner">
            <div class="header-left">
                <div class="logo">K</div>
                <div class="nav-divider"></div>
                <nav class="nav-links">
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link">Capture</a>
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link active">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link">Dossiers</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="header-right">
                <button class="header-btn">FR</button>
                <div class="avatar">TK</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">

        <!-- FEATURED PROJECT -->
        <div class="card featured animate-in">

            <!-- Radar Side -->
            <div class="radar-container">
                <svg class="radar-svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
                    <!-- Grid circles -->
                    <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="150" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="112" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="75" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="37" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>

                    <!-- Grid lines -->
                    <line x1="200" y1="50" x2="200" y2="350" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <line x1="70" y1="125" x2="330" y2="275" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                    <line x1="70" y1="275" x2="330" y2="125" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>

                    <!-- Data polygon (scores: 9, 8, 10, 8, 9, 9 out of 10) -->
                    <polygon
                        points="200,65 326,138 326,262 200,335 74,262 74,138"
                        fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)" stroke-width="1"
                    />
                    <polygon
                        points="200,65 326,138 326,262 200,335 74,262 74,138"
                        fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)" stroke-width="1"
                    />
                    <!-- Actual data shape -->
                    <polygon
                        points="200,68 318,143 318,260 200,80 82,260 82,148"
                        fill="rgba(247,81,5,0.08)"
                        stroke="#F75105"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    />
                    <!-- Corrected data polygon for scores 9,8,10,8,9,9 -->
                    <polygon
                        points="200,68 313,145 313,257 200,50 87,257 87,145"
                        fill="rgba(247,81,5,0.1)"
                        stroke="#F75105"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        opacity="0"
                    />

                    <!-- Data points -->
                    <circle cx="200" cy="68" r="4" fill="#F75105"/>  <!-- Problem 9/10 -->
                    <circle cx="318" cy="143" r="4" fill="#F75105"/> <!-- Market 8/10 -->
                    <circle cx="318" cy="260" r="4" fill="#F75105"/> <!-- Diff 10/10 -->
                    <circle cx="200" cy="335" r="4" fill="#F75105"/> <!-- Feasibility 8/10 -->
                    <circle cx="82" cy="260" r="4" fill="#F75105"/>  <!-- Business 9/10 -->
                    <circle cx="82" cy="148" r="4" fill="#F75105"/>  <!-- Founder 9/10 -->

                    <!-- Axis labels -->
                    <text x="200" y="38" text-anchor="middle" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">PROBLEME</text>
                    <text x="348" y="138" text-anchor="start" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">MARCHE</text>
                    <text x="348" y="268" text-anchor="start" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">DIFFERENCIATION</text>
                    <text x="200" y="370" text-anchor="middle" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">FAISABILITE</text>
                    <text x="52" y="268" text-anchor="end" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">BUSINESS</text>
                    <text x="52" y="138" text-anchor="end" fill="#71717A" font-size="10" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.05em" font-family="Inter">FOUNDER FIT</text>

                    <!-- Center score -->
                    <text x="200" y="192" text-anchor="middle" fill="#FAFAFA" font-size="48" font-weight="300" font-family="Inter" font-variant="tabular-nums">92</text>
                    <text x="200" y="215" text-anchor="middle" fill="#71717A" font-size="14" font-weight="400" font-family="Inter">/100</text>
                </svg>

                <div class="radar-badge">
                    <span class="badge badge-go">GO</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Details Side -->
            <div class="featured-details">
                <div class="section-label">Projet en Vedette</div>
                <h2>Drone Fleet SaaS Platform</h2>
                <p class="description">
                    A comprehensive solution for autonomous drone logistics, featuring real-time telemetry,
                    AI-driven pathfinding, and predictive maintenance. The market is expanding rapidly with
                    a CAGR of 28%.
                </p>
                <div class="separator"></div>

                <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2)">
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Probleme</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 90%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">9/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Marche</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 80%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">8/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Differenciation</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 100%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">10/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Faisabilite</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 80%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">8/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Business Model</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 90%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">9/10</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="axis-row">
                        <span class="axis-label">Founder Fit</span>
                        <div class="axis-track"><div class="axis-fill" style="width: 90%; background: var(--brand-primary)"></div></div>
                        <span class="axis-score">9/10</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="btn-row">
                    <button class="btn-primary">
                        Ouvrir le Dossier
                        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn-secondary">Enrichir l'Analyse</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CAROUSEL -->
        <div class="carousel-section animate-in delay-1">
            <div class="carousel-header">
                <h3>Autres Projets</h3>
                <div class="carousel-nav">
                    <button>&larr;</button>
                    <button>&rarr;</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-track">
                <div class="mini-card">
                    <div class="accent-band" style="background: var(--color-explore)"></div>
                    <div class="mini-title">AI Film Script Generator</div>
                    <div class="mini-desc">Leveraging LLMs for creative writing assistance. The prototype shows promise.</div>
                    <div class="mini-footer">
                        <span class="mini-score">78<span class="unit">/100</span></span>
                        <span class="badge badge-explore" style="font-size: 0.5625rem; padding: 3px 10px;">EXPLORE</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mini-card">
                    <div class="accent-band" style="background: var(--color-kill)"></div>
                    <div class="mini-title">NFT Patent Marketplace</div>
                    <div class="mini-desc">Attempting to tokenize IP rights on the blockchain. Low market demand.</div>
                    <div class="mini-footer">
                        <span class="mini-score">38<span class="unit">/100</span></span>
                        <span class="badge badge-kill" style="font-size: 0.5625rem; padding: 3px 10px;">KILL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mini-card">
                    <div class="accent-band" style="background: var(--color-park)"></div>
                    <div class="mini-title">MeowNet - Social Network for Cats</div>
                    <div class="mini-desc">Niche social network. Market size questionable despite engagement.</div>
                    <div class="mini-footer">
                        <span class="mini-score">22<span class="unit">/100</span></span>
                        <span class="badge badge-park" style="font-size: 0.5625rem; padding: 3px 10px;">PARK</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mini-card">
